// Copy this file to Secrets.xcconfig (same folder) and fill in your key.
// Get a free key at https://thecatapi.com/signup
//
// This file is already wired as the project's Base Configuration File, so
// nothing else is needed: build/run in Xcode and a "Generate API Key
// Secrets" build phase reads CAT_API_KEY from here and writes it into
// Core/Config/GeneratedSecrets.swift automatically, on every build.
//
// Secrets.xcconfig and the generated Swift file are both gitignored, so the
// key never gets committed. If you skip this step, CAT_API_KEY stays empty
// and the app still runs — just at a lower TheCatAPI rate limit.
CAT_API_KEY = your_key_here
